nse-2- 中找不到的健康功能spire-3-price-features&quot;>;Versa 4&lt;/a>; 或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23392564/fitbit-sense-2-review-google-fitness-tracker&quot;>;Fitbit Sense 2&lt;/a>;，包括水分追踪和 Garmin 的恢复功能 Body Battery。您...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/20/24301486/garmin-venu-sq-2-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/20/24301486/garmin-venu-sq-2-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/20/24301486/garmin-venu-sq-2-deal-sale</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry></feed>